# Database Rules

## Schema Location
`src/lib/db/schema.ts` — this is the SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for all tables. Read it before any DB work.

## DB Client
```typescript
import { db } from "@/lib/db";
// Uses Neon HTTP driver + Drizzle ORM. Lazy singleton, safe for serverless.
```

## Migration Workflow
1. Edit `src/lib/db/schema.ts`
2. Run `npm run db:generate` (creates SQL migration in `drizzle/`)
3. Run `npm run db:migrate` (applies to Neon)
4. NEVER edit migration SQL files directly after they've been applied

## Complete Table Reference

### Auth Tables (NextAuth)
| Table | Export | Columns |
|-------|--------|---------|
| `users` | `authUsers` | id (text PK), name, email (unique), emailVerified, image |
| `accounts` | `authAccounts` | userId, type, provider, providerAccountId (compound PK: provider+providerAccountId), refresh_token, access_token, expires_at, token_type, scope, id_token, session_state |
| `auth_sessions` | `authSessions` | sessionToken (PK), userId, expires |
| `verification_tokens` | `authVerificationTokens` | identifier, token (compound PK), expires |

