## Existing Indexes (DO NOT duplicate)
- `sessions_host_user_id_idx` on sessions(host_user_id)
- `players_session_id_idx` on players(session_id)
- `turns_session_round_started_idx` on turns(session_id, round_number, started_at)
- `actions_turn_created_idx` on actions(turn_id, created_at)
- `dice_rolls_action_id_idx` on dice_rolls(action_id)
- `scene_snapshots_session_id_idx` on scene_snapshots(session_id)
- `memory_summaries_session_id_idx` on memory_summaries(session_id)
- `narrative_events_session_created_idx` on narrative_events(session_id, created_at DESC)
- `npc_states_session_id_idx` on npc_states(session_id)
- `image_jobs_session_status_created_idx` on image_jobs(session_id, status, started_at)
- `orchestration_traces_session_created_idx` on orchestration_traces(session_id, created_at DESC)

## JSON Column Shapes
Always validate JSON data with Zod before inserting:
- `characters.stats` -> `CharacterStatsSchema` from `schemas/domain.ts`: `{ str, dex, con, int, wis, cha }` (all numbers)
- `characters.inventory` -> array of objects
- `characters.conditions` -> string array
- `characters.visual_profile` -> `Record<string, unknown>`
- `sessions.visual_bible_seed` -> `Record<string, unknown>`
- `narrative_events.visible_changes` -> string array
- `narrative_events.image_hint` -> `NarrativeImageHintSchema`: `{ subjects: string[], environment?, mood?, avoid: string[] }`
- `memory_summaries.content` -> `Record<string, unknown>`
- `actions.parsed_intent` -> `ActionIntentSchema` shape from `schemas/ai-io.ts`

## Query Patterns
```typescript
// SELECT with filter
const [row] = await db.select().from(sessions).where(eq(sessions.id, id)).limit(1);

// UPDATE
await db.update(sessions).set({ status: "active" }).where(eq(sessions.id, id));

// INSERT
await db.insert(players).values({ session_id: id, user_id, seat_index: 0 });

// JOIN
const rows = await db.select().from(players)
  .innerJoin(characters, eq(players.character_id, characters.id))
  .where(eq(players.session_id, sessionId));
```

Import `eq`, `and`, `desc`, `sql` from `drizzle-orm`. Import table exports from `@/lib/db/schema`.
